HEADWORD: Piacular
<hw>Pi*ac"u*lar</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>piacularis</ets>: cf. F. <ets>piaculaire</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
